18¿é 3:25 Truly the thing that I fear comes upon me, and what I dread befalls me.
18¿é 3:26 I am not at ease, nor am I quiet; I have no rest; but trouble comes."
18¿é 4:1 Then Eliphaz the Temanite answered:
