18¿é 5:25 You shall know that your descendants will be many, and your offspring like the grass of the earth.
18¿é 5:26 You shall come to your grave in ripe old age, as a shock of grain comes up to the threshing floor in its season.
18¿é 5:27 See, we have searched this out; it is true. Hear, and know it for yourself."
18¿é 6:1 Then Job answered:
