19½Ã 64:9 Then everyone will fear; they will tell what God has brought about, and ponder what he has done.
19½Ã 64:10 Let the righteous rejoice in the LORD and take refuge in him. Let all the upright in heart glory.
19½Ã 65:1 To the leader. A Psalm of David. A Song. Praise is due to you, O God, in Zion; and to you shall vows be performed,
