19½Ã 66:1 To the leader. A Song. A Psalm. Make a joyful noise to God, all the earth;
19½Ã 66:2 sing the glory of his name; give to him glorious praise.
19½Ã 66:3 Say to God, "How awesome are your deeds! Because of your great power, your enemies cringe before you.
