19½Ã 66:20 Blessed be God, because he has not rejected my prayer or removed his steadfast love from me.
19½Ã 67:1 To the leader: with stringed instruments. A Psalm. A Song. May God be gracious to us and bless us and make his face to shine upon us, Selah
