19½Ã 84:7 They go from strength to strength; the God of gods will be seen in Zion.
19½Ã 84:8 O LORD God of hosts, hear my prayer; give ear, O God of Jacob! Selah
19½Ã 84:9 Behold our shield, O God; look on the face of your anointed.
