19½Ã 92:2 to declare your steadfast love in the morning, and your faithfulness by night,
19½Ã 92:3 to the music of the lute and the harp, to the melody of the lyre.
19½Ã 92:4 For you, O LORD, have made me glad by your work; at the works of your hands I sing for joy.
19½Ã 92:5 How great are your works, O LORD! Your thoughts are very deep!
