19½Ã 148:9 Mountains and all hills, fruit trees and all cedars!
19½Ã 148:10 Wild animals and all cattle, creeping things and flying birds!
19½Ã 148:11 Kings of the earth and all peoples, princes and all rulers of the earth!
19½Ã 148:12 Young men and women alike, old and young together!
19½Ã 148:13 Let them praise the name of the LORD, for his name alone is exalted; his glory is above earth and heaven.
19½Ã 148:14 He has raised up a horn for his people, praise for all his faithful, for the people of Israel who are close to him. Praise the LORD!
