19½Ã 150:2 Praise him for his mighty deeds; praise him according to his surpassing greatness!
19½Ã 150:3 Praise him with trumpet sound; praise him with lute and harp!
19½Ã 150:4 Praise him with tambourine and dance; praise him with strings and pipe!
